desc: Our menu changes every other week and features healthy premade food that is always gluten and dairy free!

layout.text: We're always cooking up something new here at Kathy's Table. Our chefs work hard to create delightful dishes that satisfy every taste and never get boring. The menu changes every OTHER week so check back often to see what's currently available. And of course, everything is gluten free and dairy free.
Try one of our weekly meal plans and you'll never have to worry about what's for lunch or dinner.
You are always welcome to stop by the Kathy's Table Kitchen and pick up an a la carte meal during normal business hours.
